    {
      "id": "86816e02-b3e7-4692-91f6-5bb311c5931c",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Knowledge tracing is one of the fundamental tasks using student behavioral data in Learning Analytcs. In essence it aims to infer the knowledge state of a student and how it can be leveraged in problem-solving. The paper makes a survey on the evolving landscape of knowledge tracing. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "86816e02-b3e7-4692-91f6-5bb311c5931c",
        "parent": {
