    {
      "id": "a208f171-7abb-474f-b87a-0396a00ed0f2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Moreover, the paper introduces 2 open-source algorithms. The first downloads and preprocessing of KT-related datasets. Also EduKTM implements the most common KT models. Potential future directions are also discussed in the paper.",
